Tga '''tsertit''' taɣarast nna s skaren medden ddernin ɣ tegrawin tinaḍin (decisions). Tasertit tga-tt asemsasa ger medden fad ad afen ad myaddaren ɣ tegrawin, zund tiqbilin, timdinin, neɣ timizar. Ɣ tegrawin meqqurnin, zund timizar neɣ iwenkan (mgt. n ''awenk'': state), llan medden ittsalan taɣawsa-ad, midden-ad ar asen-nettini ''imsertiten'', amagut n ''amserti''. Adjektif n tasertit iga-t ''asertan/tasertant''. Tazrawt (the study) n tsertit ɣ tesdawin isem-as tussna tasertant neɣ tasensertit, neɣ daɣ tizrawin tisertanin.

Ɣ tudert takuyasst, irem-ad n "tasertit" isnamk taɣarast s ttyawenbaḍent tmizar, d talli s ttyaweskaren isaḍufen d ilgamen.

Inna umesfelsaf agriki [[Aristot]] mas iga ufgan yan umuder asertan d is bahra mmezdayen ithiken (ethics) d tsertit.

Ɣ usegg°as n 1651, yura [[Thomas Hobbes]] ''Leviathan'', yan udlis ɣef tsertit. Yura gis mas midden zdeɣnin ɣ tegrawin, ar sennefkan, ɣ tuggt n tikkal, kra ɣ izerfan nnsen s kra n ufrag zeɣ dar tenbaḍt.

Yura [[Nikolo Makiavelli]] mas tasertit tella s izwar fad yan ad iṭṭef adwas, yamẓ gis. Inna mas bla adwas, ur dar amɣar m'ad iskar.

